RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO,B.EVENT_CODE,B.EVENT_SEQ_NO,B.MAKER_ID,B.MAKER_DT_STAMP,B.EVENT_DATE FROM OLTBS_COC_EVENT_LOG A,OLTBS_CONTRACT_EVENT_LOG B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND B.EVENT_CODE IN ('RFLR', 'RVCR', 'REWR', 'RFRV') AND B.AUTH_STATUS = 'U' ORDER BY EVENT_SEQ_NO
